# API conventions

- Prisma models: User, Group, GroupMember, Round, Leg
- Up to `Round.legsPerMember` legs per user per round (`@@unique([roundId, userId, legIndex])`); group default `Group.legsPerMember` (1–3)
- Groups always have an open round (created with the group; next round opens when the previous settles, snapshotting `legsPerMember`)
- Round auto-locks when every member has submitted `legsPerMember` legs (or at first kickoff — partial ok)
- Settlement updates GroupMember points, User totals, and round P/L
- Use transactions for multi-table settlement updates when extending
